This is a Streamlit web app that forecasts monthly milk production using an LSTM (Long Short-Term Memory) neural network. It allows users to upload milk production data, train an LSTM model, evaluate performance, and forecast future production.
Features
- Upload CSV data (`Date`, `Production` columns)
- Interactive dashboard with:
  - Region-specific unit formatting (₦/Litre, $/Gallon, €/Litre)
  - Configurable LSTM settings
  - Model training and loading options
  - Forecast visualization with confidence in results
  - MAE and RMSE error metrics
  - Downloadable CSV results
